OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774447876
OL,3,CMurder arrest after man found
OL,4,Cunconscious in street dies
OL,6,FOfficers arrested a man at the scene
OL,7,Fon suspicion of murder and he remains
OL,8,Fin custody while their investigation
OL,9,Fcontinues.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Chris Chadderton
OL,12,Fdescribed the event as a "tragic
OL,13,Fincident" and confirmed that a team of
OL,14,Fdetectives is currently piecing
OL,15,Ftogether the events leading up to the
OL,16,Fman's death.
OL,18,F"This is a tragic incident in which a
OL,19,Fman has sadly lost his life, and our
OL,20,Fthoughts are firmly with his loved
OL,21,Fones," he said.
